apos;s Called-Out People. </div><div class="t m5a8 x96 h30 ybb8 ff3 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">READ FOR THIS WEEK&apos;S STUDY: </div><div class="t m3b7 x9b h23 yb3d ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gen. 12:1-6; Acts 7:1-8; Gal. </div><div class="t m72a x92 h23 ybb9 ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3:6-9, 29; Heb. 11:9-12. </div><div class="t m2a2 x96 h30 ybba ff3 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: </div><div class="t m12f x4 h23 ybba ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Genesis 12:2. </div><div class="t m72b x96 h30 ybbb ff3 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY QUESTIONS: </div><div class="t m4d1 xcd h23 ybbb ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did the church begin? </div><div class="t m10f x96 h30 y7d8 ff3 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OUTLINE: </div><div class="t m158 x92 h23 y7d9 ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Call of Abraham (Gen. 12:1-5). </div><div class="t m122 x92 h23 y7da ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Covenant With Abraham (Gen. 15:1-18; 17:1-14). </div><div class="t m334 x92 h23 y7db ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Faith of Abraham (Heb. 11:8-10). </div><div class="t m33b x92 h23 yb08 ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Obedience of Abraham (James 2:14-26). </div><div class="t m30e x92 h23 yb09 ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Descendants of Abraham (Gal. 3:7-9). </div><div class="t m4c6 x36 h30 y4d4 ff3 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons in Braille </div><div class="t m3c8 x92 h23 yb0c ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The regular adult Sabbath School lessons are available free each </div><div class="t m2e4 x96 h23 yb0d ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">month in Braille and 16 2/3 rpm records to blind and physically </div><div class="t m140 x96 h23 yb0e ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">handicapped persons who cannot read normal ink print. This includes </div><div class="t m72c x96 h23 yb0f ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">individuals who because of arthritis, multiple sclerosis, paralysis, </div><div class="t m5bc x96 h23 yb10 ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accident, old age, and so forth, cannot hold or focus on normal ink-</div><div class="t m34b x96